3 Emphasize the word "metropolitan" in the text below.
<h1>Tokyo</h1>
<p>
Tokyo is the capital of Japan,
the most populous 
<em>
metropolitan
</em>

area in the world.
</p>

4 Highlight the word "FUN" in the text below.
<p>HTML is <mark>FUN</mark> to learn!</p>

5 Apply subscript formatting to the number "2" in the text below.
<p>H<sub>2</sub>O is the scientific term for water.</p>

6 Add a line through (strikeout) the letters "blue" in the text below.
<p>My favorite color is <del>blue</del> red.</p>


